==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: make the boat go against the current
===Idiom===
{{cmn-idiom|ts|pin=nì shuĭ xíng zhōu|pint=ni4shui3xing2zhou1|rs=辵06}}
# to diligently engage in one's studies (like a boat going against the currents)
# to go against the tide
